03cb\u003e如果条件恒假，那么无论结论是恒真还是恒假，命题都是正确的。\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e也就是说，只要我们给出一个恒假的条件，就一定可以证明出命题的正确性。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e再者，关于我们这个1+1≠2的猜想，有一点是非常重要的，我们由1+1=2这个常识证明了1+1≠2，这和这位同学的证明也是类似的，得出的结论与我们的假设矛盾。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003e这是这位同学最大而且最浅显的错误。\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e后面的证明过程中，也明显的出现了拿结论证结论的情况。不管怎么说，这篇回答算是给了我2019年写第一篇知乎的理由了。\u003c/p\u003e","editable_content":"","excerpt":"借着这个机会，我也来发表一下我的研究成果叭。我们给出猜想：如果地球是方的，那么1＋1≠2。这个命题的逆否命题是：如果1+1=2，那么地球不是方的。第二个命题显然正确，因此第一个命题显然正确，因此1+1≠2。不知道现在大二还能不能转学去清华23333333 上…","collapsed_by":"nobody","collapse_reason":"","annotation_action":[],"mark_infos":[],"relevant_info":{"is_relevant":false,"relevant_type":"","relevant_text":""},"suggest_edit":{"reason":"","status":false,"tip":"","title":"","unnormal_details":{"status":"","description":"","reason":"","reason_id":0,"note":""},"url":""},"is_labeled":false,"reward_info":{"can_open_reward":false,"is_rewardable":false,"reward_member_count":0,"reward_total_money":0,"tagline":""},"relationship":{"is_author":false,"is_authorized":false,"is_nothelp":false,"is_thanked":false,"voting":0,"upvoted_followees":[]}}],"paging":{"is_end":false,"is_start":false,"next":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/307595822/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cadmin_closed_comment%2Creward_info%2Cis_collapsed%2Cannotation_action%2Cannotation_detail%2Ccollapse_reason%2Cis_sticky%2Ccollapsed_by%2Csuggest_edit%2Ccomment_count%2Ccan_comment%2Ccontent%2Ceditable_content%2Cvoteup_count%2Creshipment_settings%2Ccomment_permission%2Ccreated_time%2Cupdated_time%2Creview_info%2Crelevant_info%2Cquestion%2Cexcerpt%2Crelationship.is_authorized%2Cis_author%2Cvoting%2Cis_thanked%2Cis_nothelp%2Cis_labeled%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.mark_infos%5B%2A%5D.url%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.author.follower_count%2Cbadge%5B%2A%5D.topics\u0026limit=1\u0026offset=47\u0026platform=desktop\u0026sort_by=default","previous":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/307595822/